電漿物理導論一



















ESS4310 Introduction to Plasma Physics I, 電漿物理導論一










Course Description:
            What is a plasma?
            Singal-Particle Motion
Two-Fluid Equations for a Plasma
Waves in the Fluid Plasma
Transport Phenomena in plasma




課程說明：
            何謂電漿、單粒子運動、電漿流體模型、線性電漿波動理論及電漿加熱研究、電漿輸送現象。  












