課程概述 Course Description
       (I) Introduction; Single particle motions; Plasmas as fluids; Waves in fluid plasmas; Introduction to plasmonics
 (II) Diffusion and resistivity  [magnetohydrodynamics (MHD) equation]; Equilibrium and stability; Introduction to kinetic theory [kinetic plasma waves and stability]; Introduction to nonlinear plasma physics  

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    (I) Introduction; Single particle motions; Plasmas as fluids; Waves in fluid plasmas; Introduction to plasmonics
(II) Diffusion and resistivity  [magnetohydrodynamics (MHD) equation]; Equilibrium and stability; Introduction to kinetic theory [kinetic plasma waves and stability]; Introduction to nonlinear plasma physics    

